vera fogwill ( [ ˈbeɾa ˈfoɣβil ] ; born 28 november 1972 in buenos aires ) is an argentine film and television actress , film director , and screenplay writer , active in the cinema of argentina .   she is the daughter of rodolfo enrique fogwill .   her first film as a director is " las mantenidas sin sueños " ( " kept and dreamless " ) in which fogwill also plays the leading role , of a drug-addicted mother .